Package: nmecr
Type: Package
Title: An implementation of peer-reviewed energy data analysis algorithms for site-specific M&V
Version: 1.0.0
Author: c(person("Sharma", "Mrinalini", email = "msharma@kw-engineering.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
			 person("Johnson", "Devan", email = "djohnson@kw-engineering.com", role = c("ctb", "cph")),
			 person("Jump", "David", email = "djump@kw-engineering.com", role = "cph")),
Description: nmecr builds statistical energy data models and provides a comprehensive assessment of model fit and prediction accuracy.
  It provides the complete portfolio of the industry standard energy data modeling algorithms and encludes an enhancement that allows 
  data modeling of energy profiles with distinct energy use regimens for improved predictive accuracies. 
License: Refer to License.txt file
BugReports: https://github.com/kW-Labs/nmecr/issues
